Package: lpmp
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python3, python3-yaml
Description: Log Pattern Matching Profiler
 A log analysis and pattern matching tool that uses user-defined YAML
 models to measure event timing and generate timing profiles from
 on-system logs or StarlingX single or multi-host collect bundles.
 Designed for KPI performance analysis, timing validation, and system
 operation profiling across multiple log sources.